{"TopicId":136744,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"What is your biggest science pet peeve in movies?","CreatedByName":"todofwar","CreatedById":160465,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-12T00:24:49Z","PageNum":27,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"VaPaL","CreatedById":150974,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-06T12:50:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222910672\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136744\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221483564474\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex_NL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 04/01/2017 at 7:14 PM, Tex_NL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAntique Scottish claymores measured between 120 and 140 cm (47\u201355\u00A0in) on average. I found several websites selling And\u00FAril (Aragorns sword) replicas. They slightly vary in length but all fall within that size range.\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo the size isn\u0027t at all that weird. Yes, it IS an extremely big sword but not as absurd as it looks at first glance..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes but a lot of this longer swords wasn\u0027t carried in scabbards. Though what limits you carring any sword in a scabbards is the length of your arm. If it\u0027s long enough for you to pull the sword out of the scabard, then you it\u0027s fine. That\u0027s why carrying a sword in the back is stupid, you can\u0027t pull it out.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/xjURzgkCuAE?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-07T06:13:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the really long ones.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cb84223f2a5556213c975c5219581cc5.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/cb/84/22/cb84223f2a5556213c975c5219581cc5.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}